snippet.title: Man Vs Baby | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
After a job looking after a high-tech mansion ended in disaster thanks to an irritating insect in Man vs Bee, Trevor Bingley (Rowan Atkinson) has left the stressful world of housesitting for the quieter life of a school caretaker. That is, until a lucrative offer to look after a luxury London penthouse over Christmas proves too tempting to resist. But on the last day of term, when no one comes to collect the Baby Jesus from the school nativity, Trevor finds himself with another undersized and very unexpected companion. With a penthouse to protect and a baby to burp, will Trevor be able to have the calm Christmas he hopes for, or will festivities descend into chaos?

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81516058

snippet.title: The Family Man S3 - Official Trailer | Raj & DK | Manoj Bajpayee, Jaideep Ahlawat | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
The Family Man Season 3 Official Trailer 

SERIES:
"The Family Man," created by Raj & DK, an edgy and thrilling series on Prime Video, follows the life of Srikant Tiwari, a seemingly ordinary middle-class man who secretly works for the Threat Assessment and Surveillance Cell( TASC), a fictional cell of the National Investigation Agency in Mumbai. Balancing the demands of his high-stakes job and his family, life proves increasingly challenging as Srikant navigates dangerous missions against terrorists while trying to be a present husband and father. As he dives deeper into the murky world of espionage, Srikant must protect his loved ones from the perils of his covert profession, all while grappling with moral dilemmas that test his integrity and loyalty.

SEASON:
Outlawed and on the run, Srikant Tiwari faces sinister forces threatening to ignite chaos in Northeast India, uncovering a conspiracy that could plunge the nation into war.

Title:
YA ZAHRA sa | یازھرا

Originally Recited & Composed by
Shahid Hussain Baltistani

Written By
Janab Mazhar Abidi & Janab Shahid Hussain Baltistani

Translations
Janab Mohsin Rizvi USA

Chorus Team
Munawar Ali Khan, Rajab Ali Khan, Amanat Ali Khan, Ghulam Abbas Khan

Audio Recorded By

Audio Mixed & Mastered 
ODS - Brother Omer Qureshi

TNA Records - Ali Arman Baltistani

Cover Design by
Zohaib Creatives

Production Team:
Jaffer Darvaish
Baqar Ali Baltistani

Muharram Album | Jamad ul Awal  2025 / 1447
Releasing Date | 14 Nov 2025


Lyrics:
---------

Fatima Zahra s.a , Fatima Zahra s.a

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Aey Meri Bibi Teray Dar Pay Istghasa Hay 
Tera Mamnoon Meri Shahzadi Ye Jahan Saara Hay 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tu Hamain Hifz Aur Amaan’n Day Day 
Apni Chadar Ka Saibaan Day Day 
Teri Qudrat Mein Kia Nahi Bibi 
Tu Jisay Chahay Do Jahan Day Day

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tujh Ko Ummat Nay Yun Sataya Hay 
Marg E Mohsin Pay Bhi Rulaya Hay 
Tujh Ko Baba Kay Baad Ummat Nay 
Haey Darbaar Main Bulaya Hay 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Boli Zahra Ali a.s Say Ya Maula 
Ghum Ye Mujh Say Nahi Saha Jata 
Qatl E Mohsin Say Barh K Mushkil Tha 
Bharay Darbaar Main Mera Jana 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a 

Jab Tha Rassi Main Murtaza a.s Ka Gala 
Imtehaan Zabt Ka Wo Tha Tera 
Haan Madina Ujar Gaya Hota 
Tu Ho Say Deti Bad Dua Zahra

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Tu Hijaab E Khuda Hay Ya Zahra s.a
Dard Teray Hain Sab Say Poshida 
Kitni Muztar Hay Kitni Zakhmi Hay 
Ya Ali a.s Jantay Hain Ya Fizza s.a

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a 
 
Aey Mohammad saww Ki Laadli Dukhtar 
Ghum Main Teray Hay Murtaza a.s Muztar 
Jis Nay Dhaaya Tha Baab Khaybar Ka 
Gir Gaya Khaak Per Wo Ye Keh Kar 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Hum Ko Her Aan Ye Nadamat Hay 
Hum Hain Mujrim Teri Adalat Hay 
Rizq Aulaad Zindagi Her Pal 
Jo Bhi Kuch Hay Teri Badolat Hay

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Qarz Makrooz Ka Ada Karde
Muflison Ka Naseeb Wah Krde
Jin Ki Gaudi Hari Ahi Bibi
Unko Aulaad Tu Ataa Karde

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Waqt E Akhir Hay Bus Mera Bibi 
Anginat Hain Meray Gunaah Bibi 
Wasta Tujh Ko Teray Bachon Ka 
Bakhshwana Meray Gunaah Bibi 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Farsh E Majlis Pay Aur Musallay Per 
Her Jawan Keh Raha Hay Ro Ro Kar 
Hum Rahain Na Rahain Magar Bibi 
Ta Qayamat Rahay Ghum E Sarwar 

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Aey Meri Bibi Teray Bachon Ka Ghum Maantay Hain
Apni Aulad Say Kahin Bath K Ghum Ye Pyara Hay

Ya Zahra s.a Ya Zahra s.a

Gharq e Matam Shud, Alam E Baala
Mirawad Maula, Sarwar E Zahra
Aah O Waa Wailaa, Aah O Waa Wailaa

snippet.description:
Enjoy the romantic melody “Tu Mere Samne” from the movie Chori Chori. Sung by the soulful voices of Alka Yagnikand Udit Narayan, this beautiful track features Ajay Devgn, Rani Mukerji, and Sonali Bendre, perfectly capturing the essence of love and emotions in classic Bollywood style. A timeless romantic song for music lovers! 

Credits: 
Singer: Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik
Music: Sajid-Wajid 
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Chori Chori
Starring: Ajay Devgan, Sonali Bendre
Director: Milan Luthria
Producer: Lalit Kapoor, Raju Narula
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

हो हो हो हो हूँ   

तू मेरे सामने, मैं तेरे सामने   

तू मेरे सामने, मैं तेरे सामने   

मैं तेरे सामने, तू मेरे सामने   

दोनों के बीच है, मीलों की दूरियाँ   

धक धक दिल बोले मेरा, छम छम मेरी चूड़ियाँ   

हायो रब्बा हायो रब्बा, प्यार दिया मजबूरियाँ   

हायो रब्बा हायो रब्बा, प्यार दिया मजबूरियाँ   

तू मेरे सामने, मैं तेरे सामने   

मैं सोचूं हाँ कर दूँ, दिल बोले ना कर दे   

दिल बोले हाँ कर दे, मैं सोचूं ना कर दूँ   

मैं सोचूं हाँ कर दूँ, दिल बोले ना कर दे   

दिल बोले हाँ कर दे, मैं सोचूं ना कर दूँ   

रातें हैं लंबियाँ, बातें अधूरियाँ   

हाँ ना हो जाए तो हो जाए गल्ला पूरीयाँ   

हायो रब्बा हायो रब्बा, प्यार दिया मजबूरियाँ   

हायो रब्बा हायो रब्बा, प्यार दिया मजबूरियाँ   

तू मेरे सामने, मैं तेरे सामने   

हो हो हो हो हूँ   

जा अपने दामन को, फूलों से तू भर ले   

जीना है तो जी ले, मरना है तो मर ले

snippet.title: Moana | Official Teaser

#Moana, arriving only in theaters July 10, 2026 🌊 Watch the new teaser now!

In Disney’s live-action adaptation of the beloved Oscar®-nominated animated adventure, Moana (Catherine Lagaʻaia) answers the Ocean’s call and, for the first time, voyages beyond the reef of her island of Motunui with the infamous demigod Maui (Dwayne Johnson) on an unforgettable journey to restore prosperity to her people. The film is directed by Emmy® and Tony Award® winner Thomas Kail (“Hamilton”); produced by Dwayne Johnson, Dany Garcia, Beau Flynn, Hiram Garcia and Lin-Manuel Miranda; and executive produced by Thomas Kail, Scott Sheldon, Charles Newirth and Auliʻi Cravalho, who voiced Moana in the animated features “Moana” and “Moana 2.” Audiences can experience the brilliant cinematic sights, sounds and songs of “Moana” in U.S. theaters on July 10, 2026.
